  "texts": [
    "By comparing the F1 score in Table 9, TASO-BERT-CRF shows better results on the REST15 dataset, and TASO-BERT-CRF performs better on the REST16 dataset.",
    "Cai et al. (2021b) proposed Extract-Classify-ACOS for the task of ACOSQE.",
    "The method involves first-extract-then-classify two steps: aspect-opinion co-extraction and categorysentiment prediction.",
    "The first step involves inserting two [CLS] tokens at the beginning and end of the review sentence and feeding it to BERT to obtain context-aware token representations.",
    "The explicit aspect-opinion co-extraction is based on a CRF layer with the modified BIO tagging scheme."
  ],
